!     PURPOSE--DEFINE THE LABEL OFFSETS
!              FOR ANY OF THE 5 LABELS.
!              THE LABEL OFFSET SWITCHES FOR THE LABELS
!              ARE CONTAINED IN THE VARIABLES--
!                    PX1LOF,PX2LOF,PX3LOF,PY1LOF,PY2LOF
